&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a motivated Mortgage Loan Officer committed to playing an integral role on the Florida Gulf Coast East team. In this role, you will provide exceptional customer service and develop strong working relationships with internal and external customers. You will be responsible for proactively soliciting new residential mortgage business and selling Victory Mortgage products.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;You will thrive in this role if you:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoy prospecting, presenting to, listening to, and closing our customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Posses a persuasive communication style to obtain buy-in from customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate a great deal of change, pressure, and shifting priorities to accomplish your goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Desire to connect and build valuable relationships with new individuals frequently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
