&lt;li&gt;Prospect new mortgage lending opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meet with customers as necessary during various stages of the loan process, both inside and outside of the office.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize training material, reference tools and other resources to provide accurate and up-to-date loan program/ policy information to external customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure exceptional customer experiences by overseeing the loan process from origination to close and providing on-going communication to customers.&lt;/li&gt;
