&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Have patience and take a customer-centered approach to your work while maintaining control of the sales process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
