&lt;p&gt;As a Family Office Personal Assistant with Fischer Management, LLC, you will provide high-touch administrative, logistical, and personal support to multiple family households and the Family Office. This role is ideal for someone who is highly organized, discreet, service-minded, and comfortable managing a wide variety of day-to-day needs with professionalism and sound judgment.&lt;br&gt;One of the most rewarding parts of this role is serving as a trusted point of coordination for family members, household needs, appointments, travel, vendors, records, events, and personal requests while maintaining the highest level of confidentiality and responsiveness.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;You will thrive in this role if you:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
