&lt;li&gt;Maintain discretion and professionalism when handling confidential family, household, and business information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can manage shifting priorities, competing deadlines, and time-sensitive requests with sound judgment.&lt;/li&gt;
